title: 3 young children found stabbed to death in Reseda; mother arrested in Central California I ABC7
author: ABC7
description:
Three young children were found stabbed to death Saturday morning in a Reseda apartment, authorities said, prompting a search that resulted in their mother's arrest in Central California.

https://abc7.com/3-children-found-fatally-stabbed-in-reseda-mother-arrested/10505464/

localize.description:
土曜日の朝、リセダのアパートで3人の幼い子供が刺殺されているのが発見され、当局が捜索した結果、母親が逮捕されました（カリフォルニア州中部）。

https://abc7.com/3-children-found-fatally-stabbed-in-reseda-mother-arrested/10505464/
localize.title: リセダで幼児3人の刺殺体が発見され、母親が逮捕される I ABC7

localize.description:
